its and release them in the map!\nThe left and right sticks allow you to move the user's position slightly.\n\n[Type of Units]\n-Base\nThis is the Base.\nBuild your Base stronger!!\n\n-Fighter\nA common flying unit.\nGround & Air Attack.\n\n-Factory\nA factory unit.\nIt generates cash.\n\n-Bomber\nA flying unit skilled for\nbombing and ground attack.\n\n-Tank\nAn anti-ground unit.\nAttacks with rapid fire.\n\n-Anti-aircraft Artillery\nA placement unit using missles.\nEffective to flying units.\n\n-Sheild\nA placement unit for defense.\nIt has high durability.\n", "short_description": "Let's play a VR video game with your girl friend!\nThis time it's a strategy game.\nPick up the units and release them in the map.\nThe units will start fighting automatically."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "PdpArt_3000x900_JP.png", "id": "266102791924715", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974650_266102795258048_1135847423250422851_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ml574NFp4zMQ7kNvgE79zBK&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Aijh5sKf8gArnn2t7Tyc491&oh=00_AYC3iPRBQvLSyFTH351-EXn3kScTrLaQz8E_1PRD6QBDbA&oe=66DC34B4"}, {"file_name": "Art_1008x1440.png", "id": "4244000545622202", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974522_4244000548955535_6121386002098751284_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=CfTXJ-9f8SAQ7kNvgHhQucl&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Aijh5sKf8gArnn2t7Tyc491&oh=00_AYDDzFk-HvtyVzXJQYqTfFhEr6tt7TkcUcqnjCPFHAQGyg&oe=66DC1D05"}, {"file_name": "Art_2560x1440.png", "id": "3609745079249612", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974800_3609745082582945_8822499596742085698_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=IHC1lDmekkYQ7kNvgG3EI6g&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Aijh5sKf8gArnn2t7Tyc491&oh=00_AYBBYfiIvAeIhsthu2ecaEqdcRzzUYqtDIhsz4pUTwgsCw&oe=66DC4D0C"}, {"f